===Noun===
'''chalk''' (''[[uncountable]] and [[countable]]; plural'' '''chalks''')

# {{uncountable}} A soft, white, [[powdery]] [[limestone]].
# {{countable}} A piece of chalk, or, more often, processed compressed chalk, that is used for drawing and for writing on a [[blackboard]].
# [[Tailor's chalk]].
# {{uncountable}} (''climbing'') A white powdery substance used to prevent hands slipping from holds when climbing.<!--Isn't this the same as the first def?-->
# {{US}},{{military}},{{countable}} A [[platoon]]-sized group of [[airborne]] [[soldier]]s
